sent.body: I got the info but wanted to know more about the preset programs.   The net advertisement shows 20 preset programs, but the info I received only shows 4. Also how fast does this machine get to.   This machine has a 10 year warrrenty.   Who willl service this in Texas and If for any reason treadmilll by net ceases to exist, what are the conditions of my warrrenty.On the preset programs can I just say I want to run X distance whether it is a hilll workout, time or what ever?What is the maximum amount of time a workout can be programmmed to?Are there only 10 segments even in a user defined program?   If I wanted 20 intervals in an interval workout is that posssible?   If I wanted to run for an hour, does each segment have to be 6 minutes?Tom Donohoe
